# Trivy ignore file
#
# Format: one CVE / misconfig ID per line. Anything after `#` is a
# comment. Document *why* a finding is suppressed so reviewers can
# revisit when the upstream advisory changes.

# AVD-DS-0002: Dockerfile.dev runs as root.
# Production `Dockerfile` already runs as `appuser` (non-root). The
# dev image is only used by docker compose for local development with
# bind-mounted source — switching to non-root requires matching the
# container UID to the host UID (build args, compose changes, macOS
# vs Linux verification). Tracked in #59.
AVD-DS-0002
